This paper primarily focuses on the correlation between personality traits and susceptibility to phishing attacks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The study also examines how these factors affect users' behavior on Facebook, which could fall under social networking (cs.SI) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses privacy settings on Facebook, which could fall under cybersecurity (cs.CY) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
